# Keep Docker build context small and exclude secrets from images.

# Dependencies & build outputs
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/build
**/.next
**/out
**/.turbo
**/coverage
**/.nyc_output

# Environment & secrets (never bake into images)
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example

# Git & VCS
.git
.gitignore
.gitattributes

# Editors / OS / Claude
.vscode
.idea
.claude
.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store

# Logs
**/*.log
**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-*.log*

# Docs & misc not needed in images
ai/
docs/
*.md
!apps/api/README.md
!apps/web/README.md

# Test config not needed at runtime
**/test/
**/__tests__/
**/*.spec.ts
**/*.test.ts
